    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Inclined, sometimes foldable supports, made of wood or metal, on which a missal or other liturgical book is placed on the altar. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
